Package: ngrok
Version: 3.39.1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: wget, proot, openssl
Section: net
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://ngrok.com
Description: Secure tunnels to localhost
 ngrok is a cross-platform application that exposes local
 development servers to the internet with secure tunnels.
 Features include introspection, replay, and replay of
 requests for webhook testing and debugging.
